*uuidtools-2.0.0 (25 Aug 2009)

  25 Aug 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +uuidtools-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  04 May 2009; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  uuidtools-1.0.7-r1.ebuild:
  Fix src_test when Ruby 1.9 is not present.

*uuidtools-1.0.7-r1 (27 Apr 2009)

  27 Apr 2009; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/uuidtools-1.0.7+ruby-1.8.7.patch, +uuidtools-1.0.7-r1.ebuild:
  Add a fix for uuidtools with Ruby 1.8.7's securerandom and make it install
  for Ruby 1.9 too.

  19 Apr 2009; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> uuidtools-1.0.7:
  amd64/x86 stable, bug #266508

  17 Apr 2009; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -uuidtools-1.0.4.ebuild:
  Remove 1.0.4 version (old version with gem).

  12 Mar 2009; Alex Legler <a3li@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Removing flameeyes from metadata, as per his request.

  07 Dec 2008; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add long description.

